Task:01

1.Change your working directory to /root
2.Then, copy the file school to /tmp

Advices:

Don’t forget to validate your current working directory
Don’t forget to display the list of files of your current directory to validate the copy of the file

Resolution:

cd /root
cp /root/school /tmp

cd = change directory
cp = copy files or directories 
	Syntax:
	cp [location_file] [destination]
Example:
	cd /root/school /tmp
	
